{#-
  Card — surface container with optional header / body / footer slots.

  Composed via Twig {% embed %} blocks (header / body / footer). Each
  block is optional — a body-only Card is just a padded surface; a
  header-only Card is a heading on a surface; a full Card has all three.

  Hoverable (opt-in via prop):
    - hoverable: false (default) → static surface.
    - hoverable: true → on hover, shadow lifts to `--shadow-2`, border
      darkens to `--color-border-strong`, cursor switches to `pointer`.
      The Card itself is NOT a button — interactive Cards (a Card-as-link
      or Card-as-button) are deferred to Ring 2 `LinkCard` Compound. The
      `hoverable` prop just paints the affordance; the consumer wraps the
      whole Card in an `<a>` or `<button>` if the entire surface should
      activate.

  Variants:
    - surface (default) — flat bg-elevated card on bg-base; `--shadow-card`
      (= shadow-1, subtle).
    - elevated — same bg but `--shadow-popover` (= shadow-3, lifted).
    - subtle — bg-base + 1px border-subtle (lowest emphasis, e.g. setting
      cards inside a settings tab).

  Zero Stimulus controller.

  Parameters:
    variant     (string, optional)  — surface (default) | elevated | subtle
    hoverable   (bool,   optional)  — false (default) | true
    className   (string, optional)

  Blocks (all optional):
    header — heading + optional kebab-menu / status / actions
    body   — main content (the typical reason a Card exists)
    footer — actions / metadata / link "Voir plus"

  If no block is provided, the Card renders as an empty padded surface
  (useful as a base for composition higher up — e.g. a DataTable cell).
-#}

{%- set variant   = variant   | default('surface') -%}
{%- set hoverable = hoverable | default(false) -%}
{%- set className = className | default('') -%}
{%- set attrs       = attrs       | default({}) -%}
{%- set headerClass = headerClass | default('') -%}
{%- set bodyClass   = bodyClass   | default('') -%}
{%- set footerClass = footerClass | default('') -%}
{%- set htmlId      = htmlId      | default(null) -%}

{%- set _classes = ['cremona-card'] -%}
{%- if variant == 'elevated' -%}{%- set _classes = _classes | merge(['cremona-card--elevated']) -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if variant == 'subtle' -%}{%- set _classes = _classes | merge(['cremona-card--subtle']) -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if hoverable -%}{%- set _classes = _classes | merge(['cremona-card--hoverable']) -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if className -%}{%- set _classes = _classes | merge([className]) -%}{%- endif -%}

<article class="{{ _classes | join(' ') }}" data-variant="{{ variant }}"{% if htmlId %} id="{{ htmlId }}"{% endif %}{% for _n, _v in attrs if _n not in ['class', 'id'] %} {{ _n }}="{{ _v }}"{% endfor %}>
  {%- if block('header') is defined and block('header') is not empty -%}
    <header class="cremona-card__header{% if headerClass %} {{ headerClass }}{% endif %}">{%- block header -%}{%- endblock -%}</header>
  {%- endif -%}
  {%- if block('body') is defined and block('body') is not empty -%}
    <div class="cremona-card__body{% if bodyClass %} {{ bodyClass }}{% endif %}">{%- block body -%}{%- endblock -%}</div>
  {%- endif -%}
  {%- if block('footer') is defined and block('footer') is not empty -%}
    <footer class="cremona-card__footer{% if footerClass %} {{ footerClass }}{% endif %}">{%- block footer -%}{%- endblock -%}</footer>
  {%- endif -%}
</article>
